# REGISTER an Account

## Method: POST

## URL

> [http://localhost:3000](https://rent-note.vercel.app) 


## Request Example

> POST [http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register](http://localhost:3000/api/v1/task) 


## Parameter(resource)

1. task: check task data


## Response

